pullRequest.title: Add blighted food/pots from bounty hunter to itemstats plugin
pullRequest.bodyText:
Adds the blighted food/pots introduced with the bounty hunter update to the itemstats plugin.
Blighted anglerfish, manta ray, karambwan, and super restore(1)-(4).

commit.message: Add blighted food/pots from bounty hunter
Standardise tab usage and condense super restore/angler variants
Standardise entry orders for blighted variants (blighted always after regular)
